<p>&nbsp;Breco Lights Nigeria Co., Limited, established in Lagos in 2010, is a professional LED lighting supplier and solutions provider. The company began large-scale distribution under the Eurolight brand in 2014, and its expertise has earned strong recognition among commercial and industrial engineering clients. With two major warehouses in Lagos, Breco Lights can supply a full range of LED lighting products quickly and efficiently. Their portfolio includes commercial and industrial lighting, outdoor solutions, and accessories such as floodlights, high bay lights, modular street lights, LED panels, spotlights, solar-powered luminaires, motion sensors, garden lights, and lighting control systems.</p>
<p>&nbsp;Breco Lights is the exclusive agent of GRNLED in Nigeria, with OEM production managed by Greenriy Technology Co., Limited. All inquiries, installations, and after-sales services within Nigeria are handled directly by Breco Lights. Eurolight represents the combined strengths of both companies, merging production expertise with localized sales and support to deliver high-quality LED lighting solutions across Nigeria and the broader African market.</p>
<p>&nbsp;Eurolight is committed to providing efficient, durable, and high-standard electrical and LED lighting products. Beyond supplying lighting equipment, the brand offers consulting and complete project-based lighting solutions tailored to commercial and industrial applications. The mission is to help customers create spaces that are visually appealing, functional, and aligned with modern lighting standards.</p>
<p>&nbsp;The company operates with a strict service philosophy defined by three principles: no low-quality LED products, no dishonesty toward customers, and no unrealistic promises. Through continuous innovation and collaboration with clients, Eurolight delivers long-term value and reliable solutions. As of May 2025, the brand offers more than 60 tailored solutions across residential, commercial, industrial, and outdoor landscape lighting, serving numerous prominent enterprises throughout Nigeria.</p>
